== Additional Information == In {{ill|1997|ja|平成9th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1997|qq=}}, a statue of Shōni Suketoki riding a horse, sculpted by {{ill|Koganemaru Ikku|ja|小金丸幾久|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koganemaru Ikku|qq=}}, was erected in front of the Ashibe Ferry Terminal to commemorate the 720th anniversary of the {{ill|Mongol invasions of Japan|ja|元寇|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mongol invasions of Japan|qq=}}.
