== Additional Information == In {{ill|1997|ja|平成9年|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1997|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1997年}}[[Category:Years needing redirect replacements]], a statue of Shōni Suketoki riding a horse, sculpted by {{ill|Koganemaru Ikku|ja|小金丸幾久|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koganemaru Ikku|qq=}}, was erected in front of the Ashibe Ferry Terminal to commemorate the 720th anniversary of the [[:en:Mongol invasions of Japan|Mongol invasions of Japan]].
